## Claude's Processing Rules

### When Starting a Session

1. **Check Prompts first** — Look for `status: pending` items
2. **Scan Thoughts** — Look for actionable items since last check
3. **Review Ideas** — If working on related project, check for relevant ideas

### After Processing

Claude adds completion notes to processed items:

**For Thoughts:**
```markdown
> [!PROCESSED] 2025-12-14
> **Action:** Created task file for implementation
> **Output:** [[tasks/feature-name.md]]
```

**For Prompts:**
```markdown
> [!done] Completed 2025-12-14
> **Result:** Summary of what was done
> **Output:** [[path/to/output]]
```

